    "en": {
      "title": "A meeting between Minister Dhammika and Chinese Ambassador",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting between Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Chi Shenhon and Minister of Investment Promotion Dhammika Perera took place at the Chinese Embassy in Colombo yesterday (29).",
        "Economic and trade issues between China and Sri Lanka as well as active Chinese investment in Sri Lanka were discussed.",
        "The Chinese embassy said on its Twitter account that they also discussed a number of issues of mutual interest."
      ],
